@base <https://w3id.org/utoronto/ontologies/SeisFront#> .

<https://w3id.org/utoronto/ontologies/SeisFront> rdf:type owl:Ontology ;
                                                  owl:imports <http://www.ontology-of-units-of-measure.org/resource/om-2/subset> ,
